官陳廣池早前在其他案件的聆訊上透露，他是國安法指定法官之一。陳官甫開庭即提及，法官郭偉健於去年1月本案提訊時，頒令禁止任何人包括傳媒報道任何可能導致公眾識別現年15歲女被告身份的事項，包括但不限於姓名、住址、學校名稱，直至法庭另行頒令。<br />\n<br />\n辯方向陳官確認，申請頒令是基於被告的年齡。陳官聞言即稱，留意到最近有不少性質相近的審訊都有類似命令，惟為「公平起見，一視同仁」，表明會撤銷該命令，控辯雙方對此均沒陳詞。陳官沒有明言其決定是要對哪一方公平而作出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/RD7QIB57CNHMBC2LEV572VKHFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FRD7QIB57CNHMBC2LEV572VKHFI%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCSwfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=f6083467\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FRD7QIB57CNHMBC2LEV572VKHFI%2F&h=198ce625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/RD7QIB57CNHMBC2LEV572VKHFI/</a>"},{"pid":"dc0c269a8c881770651ab84e300682946fb47918","tid":2370444,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26eaead98797ac5e1982f8b9fa23985b8620a924","tid":2370444,"uid":34811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"有輕度弱智的送貨工人，往車房送貨時被指半年前爆竊車房3萬元，工人否認指控，其僱主亦出示更表，證明工人案發當日並未出車送貨，政府及辯方專家亦指工人屬智障人士，惟原審法官<span class=\"red\">陳廣池</span>仍堅信工人有罪，判他入獄22月。工人提出上訴，上訴庭今（8日）認為原審官無理由拒絕接受工人是智障人士，裁工人上訴得直，即時釋放，不用重審。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"成班賤種狗賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0972a41e941117704f9aed0f09c6c2d983eb2b","tid":2370444,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:35:46.000Z","msg":"淨色黃色已經夠玩啦"},{"pid":"3c3e32c2d9c686f42cefd6d7364c9dc1f0d8ed39","tid":2370444,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:40:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">辯方大律師盤問期間， #陳廣池法官 多次打斷律師盤問，指「法庭未問完，辯方唔准插嘴。問問題要有時段，啲辯方大律師成日都係咁，唔容許。」<br />\n<br />\n🌟PW2同意在口供及記事冊中都沒有提及銀色硬物上有橡筋只是寫「左手持銀色硬物」，但在庭上作供時就指見到銀色硬物上有橡筋。辯方大律師質疑PW2在證人台上捏造當時所見。 #陳廣池法官 指「點解要問呢條問題？口供同記事冊冇講唔等於唔存在㗎，你挑戰緊證人品格你知架可？」辯方大律師指為證人可信性，非其品格， #陳廣池法官 續指「係兩回事，你話佢作故仔喎，有冇理解錯？我提一提你啫。」</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e5d8534c9936e44e4a321c2f58983a2d320faef0","tid":2370444,"uid":27986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9faa14138447802387b00412e3af6bbf873f7b80","tid":2370444,"uid":34811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1c33ee85da6f83fd925302caa9e0e8678f69ab4","tid":2370444,"uid":27986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16a214353e0222821cb352ebc0c60f24658cb8cf","tid":2370444,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"池記好官嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"危駕車死人判4個月<br />\n你話好唔好官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73412384c1800ee75373e325f11ca351c9053705","tid":2370444,"uid":27986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82b1e7540394c3b54661681b388995c4af58ca0","tid":2370444,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1c33ee85da6f83fd925302caa9e0e8678f69ab4","tid":2370444,"uid":27986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16a214353e0222821cb352ebc0c60f24658cb8cf","tid":2370444,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/